0:02:24.400,0:02:29.160
Coua, who do you think is going to be found out?

0:02:29.580,0:02:31.880
It must be the one who victimized Lady Vertu.

0:02:31.920,0:02:35.500
It's a pity that Consort Fleur is still unaware.

0:02:36.160,0:02:38.420
"One may have more dreams over a long night."

0:02:38.420,0:02:41.420
Maybe His Majesty's anger will dissipate by the morning.

0:02:43.180,0:02:45.500
What do you think she'll do when she finds out what happened?

0:02:45.800,0:02:47.260
You know her.

0:02:47.380,0:02:49.280
She will either go to Great General Nian,

0:02:49.380,0:02:53.400
or kill Liu Ben immediately and then cry for His majesty's mercy.

0:02:54.440,0:02:58.460
True, if she finds out tonight she will create chaos, and infuriate His Majesty.

0:02:59.480,0:03:01.640
When we passed the Palace of Earthly Honor,

0:03:01.660,0:03:03.600
it was very quiet, wasn't it?

0:03:03.860,0:03:05.240
Yes, it was.

0:03:05.740,0:03:07.860
She is used to controlling the harem.

0:03:08.100,0:03:10.580
But now, My Lady ...

0:03:10.920,0:03:12.980
It is you who controls when she finds out  ...

0:03:13.380,0:03:14.540
Go quickly then.

0:03:14.660,0:03:16.540
To the Palace of Earthly Honor?

0:03:19.260,0:03:22.340
Your Highness looked through the
medical books all day at the Imperial Infirmary.

0:03:22.340,0:03:23.940
And you haven't stop reading since you came back.

0:03:23.960,0:03:27.960
It's getting late now. Your Highness should take a break.

0:03:28.460,0:03:30.900
Your eyes are red and tired.

0:03:31.460,0:03:33.100
Why do you have so much time to talk?

0:03:33.160,0:03:34.460
Go get a few more candles.

0:03:35.500,0:03:36.620
Yes.

0:03:36.840,0:03:40.180
Your Majesty, terrible news... Liu Ben has been arrested.

0:03:41.460,0:03:43.620
What? Liu Ben was caught?

0:03:43.960,0:03:45.820
By whom? And where is he now?

0:03:46.000,0:03:47.260
I have no idea.

0:03:47.260,0:03:50.660
I just heard Attendant An's maid
talking to one of our maids about it.

0:03:51.740,0:03:53.780
Attendant An?

0:03:54.540,0:03:56.620
So it was Zhen Huan.

0:03:58.460,0:04:02.460
Could the assassins have been more useless?
Liu Ben is just a weak doctor.

0:04:03.800,0:04:05.060
Your Highness must stay calm.

0:04:05.060,0:04:08.020
Since Liu Ben has been arrested
he must confessed.

0:04:08.780,0:04:12.740
Instead of being angry, Your Highness
needs to calm down and think of a plan.

0:04:14.920,0:04:17.040
Go! Go tell my brother ...

0:04:17.220,0:04:20.440
Your Highness, the palace gates have already been locked.

0:04:21.860,0:04:23.420
If His Majesty is enraged,

0:04:23.480,0:04:26.720
even the Great General can't interfere with His Majesty's harem.

0:04:28.980,0:04:30.740
What should I do?

0:04:30.940,0:04:32.800
I can't just sit around here.

0:04:34.000,0:04:35.740
We are all in the same boat.

0:04:35.740,0:04:40.200
The two brothers from the Jiang family can't escape this.

0:04:41.140,0:04:42.760
-Zhou Ninghai.
-Yes.

0:04:42.760,0:04:44.740
Tell them to keep their mouths shut.

0:04:46.300,0:04:49.820
Go tell His Majesty in the early morning 
 that I am gravely ill.

0:04:51.500,0:04:55.200
I can only hope that will make His Majesty more lenient.

0:04:56.360,0:04:59.060
I understand. I will go right away.

0:05:00.840,0:05:04.480
It's necessary to keep the two doctors quiet.

0:05:04.820,0:05:06.580
But if Your Highness wants His Majesty to relent,

0:05:06.580,0:05:09.820
your long mutual affection is not enough.

0:05:10.320,0:05:13.460
Your Highness must give him what he wants the most now.

0:05:14.880,0:05:19.020
His Majesty will punish Your Highness
because Your Highness made a mistake.

0:05:19.500,0:05:22.240
A mistake deserves punishment, but a feat deserves reward.

0:05:23.320,0:05:27.000
If Your Highness can atone for the mistake by performing a great feat,

0:05:27.020,0:05:31.580
His Majesty will have a reason
to also prevent gossip about Your Highness.

0:05:38.420,0:05:40.820
I won't unfairly forgive a crime.

0:05:42.200,0:05:44.460
Go announce my decree to the Palace of Earthly Honor.

0:05:44.960,0:05:47.240
Yes, I'll do it now.

0:05:48.700,0:05:51.420
Every day I am consumed with worry about the plague at court.

0:05:52.120,0:05:53.800
I don't know if it will ever end.

0:05:54.400,0:05:57.140
"The strong work with their arms,
while the wise exert their minds."

0:05:57.320,0:06:00.020
Your Majesty is especially tired,
exhausting your arms and your mind.

0:06:00.440,0:06:04.600
Hearing you say that, I feel as if my bitter 
 work is as sweet as honey.

0:06:06.360,0:06:08.520
I didn't speak properly last night.

0:06:08.840,0:06:10.280
Don't take it to heart.

0:06:10.860,0:06:12.540
I dare not.

0:06:19.780,0:06:21.620
- Peace to Your Highness.
- Rise.

0:06:22.780,0:06:23.820
I need to see His Majesty.

0:06:23.820,0:06:26.020
His Majesty is about to leave for court.

0:06:26.220,0:06:27.820
I was just heading for the Palace of Earthly Honor.

0:06:27.820,0:06:30.340
That may be, but I have an urgent request for an audience.

0:06:30.920,0:06:32.060
Your Highness.

0:06:32.060,0:06:34.480
I'm afraid His Majesty is too busy to see you.

0:06:34.963,0:06:37.140
His Majesty can decide whether to see me or not.

0:06:37.140,0:06:39.200
Your job is to inform him.

0:06:40.940,0:06:43.160
Just a moment, Your Highness.

0:06:50.560,0:06:51.880
Your Majesty...

0:06:51.940,0:06:53.200
Concubine Fleur ...

0:06:53.220,0:06:54.660
Concubine Nian is here.

0:06:54.940,0:06:56.280
She requests an audience with Your Majesty.

0:06:56.280,0:06:57.540
What's the matter?

0:06:57.620,0:07:00.540
Concubine Nian came with Dr Jiang Cheng and Dr Jiang Shen.

0:07:01.024,0:07:03.948
She insists on seeing Your Majesty.
It seems to be something urgent.

0:07:05.020,0:07:06.840
Did you announce my decree?

0:07:07.060,0:07:10.520
Concubine Nian came in a rush,
and did not allow me to say anything.

0:07:11.620,0:07:14.260
If not, stop calling her "Concubine Nian".

0:07:15.600,0:07:17.620
Tell them to wait for me in the West Chamber.

0:07:18.060,0:07:19.000
Yes.

0:07:28.180,0:07:29.840
His Majesty is here.

0:07:30.320,0:07:32.220
I bow in respect before Your Majesty

0:07:35.720,0:07:37.360
Peace and grace to Consort Fleur.

0:07:39.240,0:07:40.900
- All rise.
- I thank Your Majesty.

0:07:41.980,0:07:43.300
What's so urgent?

0:07:43.576,0:07:45.074
I have great news for Your Majesty.

0:07:45.099,0:07:49.901
Drs. Jiang Cheng and Jiang Zhen have found a remedy for the plague.

0:07:50.500,0:07:53.300
I brought them here to report to Your Majesty.

0:07:54.340,0:07:55.280
Really?

0:07:55.280,0:07:58.060
Yes, but I am not well-versed in medicine.

0:07:58.440,0:08:00.320
I will let them explain to Your Majesty.

0:08:04.180,0:08:07.200
The six evil Qi, "wind, cold, summer-heat, damp, dryness, and fire",

0:08:07.320,0:08:11.180
invade through the nose and overrun the Upright Qi.

0:08:11.336,0:08:15.537
They attack the Upper Burner, Lung and Stomach,
and creates turmoil in the organs.

0:08:15.560,0:08:17.440
Don't be a pedant. Get to the point.

0:08:17.680,0:08:19.900
In most cases, the plague is caused by unsanitary food,

0:08:20.220,0:08:22.080
which damages the Spleen, Stomach, and Intestines.

0:08:22.500,0:08:25.520
We pored over the ancient medical books, and developed a prescription.

0:08:25.940,0:08:27.780
We call it the Plague Emergency Relief Formula.

0:08:28.000,0:08:31.480
It's warm nature dispels damp, and tonicifies Liver, Kidney, and innate qi.

0:08:32.180,0:08:35.100
Has it been examined by all the imperial doctors?
Is it effective?

0:08:35.620,0:08:36.480
It has.

0:08:36.540,0:08:41.580
Two eunuchs already took the formula,
and their fever broke after two doses.

0:08:42.660,0:08:43.980
Good.

0:08:45.520,0:08:46.760
Good.

0:08:49.340,0:08:50.880
Your Highness.

0:08:52.660,0:08:55.060
I beg Your Majesty's pardon.

0:08:55.900,0:08:58.380
Are you feeling unwell? Take a seat.

0:08:58.560,0:08:59.720
I thank Your Majesty.

0:08:59.720,0:09:03.180
When Her Highness heard that the remedy
might be found in old medical books,

0:09:03.620,0:09:05.520
she stayed up all night going through the books.

0:09:05.840,0:09:10.200
Her Highness is also feeling weak because she
stayed up until early morning the last few days.

0:09:11.300,0:09:14.140
I know I am unworthy of serving Your Majesty

0:09:14.420,0:09:16.280
and always make Your Majesty angry.

0:09:16.600,0:09:20.900
But I would do anything to ease Your Majesty's burdens.

0:09:22.480,0:09:24.220
My beloved Consort has worked tirelessly.

0:09:26.580,0:09:28.420
- Su Peisheng.
- Your Majesty.

0:09:28.420,0:09:30.680
Take some servants and go with Dr Jiang.

0:09:31.638,0:09:33.788
Deliver the herbs immediately to Lady Vertu.

0:09:34.623,0:09:37.133
And then distribute it to everyone else infected.

0:09:37.560,0:09:38.620
Yes.

0:09:48.100,0:09:49.160
Lady Vertu?

0:09:49.300,0:09:50.260
Yes.

0:09:50.700,0:09:53.620
I have restored Companion Shen's title

0:09:55.280,0:09:58.440
of which she was wrongfully deprived.

0:09:59.820,0:10:01.660
Shen must have suffered a lot.

0:10:02.800,0:10:04.940
She deserves compensation from Your Majesty.

0:10:07.220,0:10:08.980
Such happy news, Lady Sourire!

0:10:09.000,0:10:11.720
You and your sister don't need to worry anymore.

0:10:14.760,0:10:16.560
I thank Your Highness.

0:10:18.600,0:10:21.720
I dare not ask for Your Majesty's forgiveness 
of my impetuous mistakes in the past.

0:10:22.180,0:10:26.420
I wish only that Your Majesty's good health
has not been harmed by the anger I have caused.

0:10:27.380,0:10:30.040
I am a humble commoner like "the roadside grass"

0:10:30.040,0:10:32.900
while Your Majesty's health is critical to everyone under Heaven.

0:10:33.300,0:10:35.140
All right.

0:10:35.460,0:10:38.200
You have made a great contribution to the country today.

0:10:39.520,0:10:42.420
If the medicine can cure the plague,

0:10:42.940,0:10:45.040
then everyone under Heaven will benefit.

0:10:45.340,0:10:48.340
My decision about awards and punishments will be fair.

0:10:50.880,0:10:52.880
I thank Your Majesty.

0:11:06.100,0:11:08.820
My Lady....

0:11:08.820,0:11:10.600
My Lady.

0:11:10.920,0:11:16.360
Do I still need to deliver His Majesty's
decree on Consort Fleur and the two doctors?

0:11:18.300,0:11:20.700
I know I should be asking His Majesty...

0:11:20.900,0:11:22.980
But since you were there, My Lady,

0:11:23.400,0:11:25.900
I humbly seek your guidance.

0:11:27.680,0:11:29.460
It seems to me that ...

0:11:29.940,0:11:31.640
you don't have to go, sir.

0:11:32.400,0:11:34.560
If you end up delivering a decree,

0:11:35.000,0:11:37.760
it will be one to promote her.

0:11:53.180,0:11:56.520
Dr. Wen, Dr. Jiang asked me to send you the medicine for Lady Vertu.

0:11:56.900,0:12:00.300
Has Dr. Jiang found a cure for plague as well?

0:12:02.040,0:12:03.920
I'll have a look.

0:12:22.400,0:12:25.460
His Majesty the Emperor!

0:12:29.800,0:12:32.100
- Peace and grace to Your Majesty.
- Rise.

0:12:32.400,0:12:34.280
You're having breakfast.

0:12:34.280,0:12:36.120
How's the food?

0:12:37.060,0:12:40.080
Whether it's insipid or delicious,

0:12:40.320,0:12:41.880
it's made by the Imperial Kitchen.

0:12:41.880,0:12:43.880
I dare not be picky.

0:12:44.560,0:12:46.540
Have a seat.

0:12:49.020,0:12:51.740
The Imperial Kitchen has to prepare food for everyone.

0:12:52.320,0:12:54.500
They can't make particular compromises for one person.

0:12:54.640,0:12:56.740
Likewise, I have to consider the greater good.

0:12:57.620,0:12:59.620
Yes, I understand.

0:13:00.140,0:13:02.040
The plague has been rampant.

0:13:02.580,0:13:05.620
Consort Fleur and Dr. Jiang exerted themselves pursuing the remedy.

0:13:05.940,0:13:07.840
Her hard work makes up for her mistake.

0:13:08.180,0:13:10.580
As for Liu Ben, I have granted him suicide.

0:13:11.440,0:13:14.200
This will, to an extent, compensate Lady Vertu.

0:13:14.300,0:13:17.600
Liu Ben is not the culprit behind this.

0:13:19.720,0:13:21.340
I understand.

0:13:22.340,0:13:25.000
But I need their assistance right now.

0:13:25.340,0:13:27.500
I have not forgotten what Lady Vertu suffered.

0:13:28.060,0:13:30.300
Nor will I let them off easy.

0:13:32.440,0:13:34.340
Your Majesty's health takes priority.

0:13:34.580,0:13:36.560
There's nothing else that concerns me.

0:13:36.560,0:13:38.240
That's good.

0:13:38.540,0:13:41.400
I also hope you can understand
that I won't be around as much.

0:13:43.300,0:13:46.300
I understand that Your Majesty will be busy with state affairs.

0:13:47.400,0:13:49.060
I have to go now.

0:13:50.200,0:13:52.420
His Majesty is leaving.

0:14:01.820,0:14:03.780
His Majesty has dark circles under his eyes.

0:14:03.780,0:14:06.240
He must have been working long hours.

0:14:06.960,0:14:09.300
His Majesty did work very late last night.

0:14:10.260,0:14:12.480
Ask my kitchen to make some ginseng soup

0:14:12.760,0:14:14.980
and send it to the Hall of Mental Cultivation.

0:14:15.440,0:14:20.080
My Lady, you must understand that even
an emperor cannot do everything he wants.

0:14:21.800,0:14:25.800
In the harem, a woman's future and favor

0:14:27.180,0:14:29.680
all rest upon His Majesty's pillow.

0:14:30.300,0:14:32.920
But His Majesty's government also rests upon his pillow.

0:14:34.880,0:14:38.680
Love seems unconquerable but vanishes like smoke.

0:14:40.100,0:14:42.000
We both understand how it has to be.

0:14:42.600,0:14:44.520
That’s all too common in the palace.

0:14:44.660,0:14:46.220
My Lady, don't take it to heart.

0:14:46.420,0:14:48.200
I won't.

0:14:49.220,0:14:51.140
I'm just feeling disappointed.

0:14:52.540,0:14:54.980
I never thought His Majesty would cease to trust me.

0:14:56.440,0:14:59.100
I know His Majesty is a sensitive person.

0:15:00.820,0:15:03.740
When His Majesty wronged Meizhuang,

0:15:03.740,0:15:06.840
I wondered whether he would distrust me one day.

0:15:08.320,0:15:12.440
But now that it's happened, I'm surprised how much it saddens me.

0:15:13.980,0:15:18.540
Right and wrong are the least important among the concubines.

0:15:19.260,0:15:22.360
What matters is who His Majesty is willing to trust.

0:15:23.440,0:15:26.160
Instead of being sad, My Lady,

0:15:26.420,0:15:30.700
you have to start thinking about
how to reduce His Majesty's suspicion.

0:15:32.600,0:15:35.640
Why don’t you say "dispel His Majesty's suspicion"?

0:15:37.560,0:15:39.360
If you think you can do that, My Lady,

0:15:39.380,0:15:41.020
we can say that instead.

0:15:46.640,0:15:48.340
What happened?

0:15:49.300,0:15:52.560
What made you suddenly feel nauseous and heavy in your chest?

0:15:53.440,0:15:56.320
I thought you were in good prenatal health.

0:15:58.700,0:16:00.700
Your Majesty must not worry.

0:16:00.700,0:16:02.600
Lady Fuca simply ate too much.

0:16:02.800,0:16:04.900
It caused her chest to feel tight.

0:16:05.000,0:16:07.580
She just needs to have a lighter meal for dinner.

0:16:08.440,0:16:12.500
You could not tell the difference between being too full and being ill?

0:16:14.000,0:16:16.260
I was just scared, Your Majesty.

0:16:16.480,0:16:19.620
All right, you should lie down and have a good rest.

0:16:19.700,0:16:21.960
I still have some work to do. I’ll come back in the evening.

0:16:21.960,0:16:23.040
Your Majesty…

0:16:23.060,0:16:24.320
I know.

0:16:24.840,0:16:27.560
I said I will be here.

0:16:30.360,0:16:32.020
His Majesty is leaving.

0:16:32.300,0:16:33.920
I bid Your Majesty goodbye.

0:16:42.860,0:16:44.400
Good.

0:16:45.800,0:16:47.520
This is great!

0:16:48.360,0:16:50.680
Nian Fu lived up to my expectation.

0:16:51.060,0:16:53.280
He quelled the rebellion at Mount Zhuozi.

0:16:53.820,0:16:56.800
Like father, like son.

0:16:57.520,0:16:59.960
Your Majesty, it’s almost time for lunch.

0:17:00.280,0:17:04.400
Would Your Majesty prefer to eat at the
Hall of Mental Cultivation or in the harem?

0:17:05.260,0:17:09.820
Didn’t the Imperial Kitchen make braised quail rice pearls today?

0:17:10.340,0:17:11.820
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:17:12.100,0:17:14.360
I remember it's Consort Fleur's favorite dish.

0:17:14.400,0:17:15.720
I will eat at the Palace of Earthly Honor.

0:17:15.860,0:17:17.220
What a coincidence!

0:17:17.460,0:17:19.780
The Palace of Earthly Honor has just
sent someone to invite Your Majesty over.

0:17:20.060,0:17:23.560
We seem to share one heart and one mind.

0:17:26.140,0:17:28.940
Braised abalone with pearl eggs,
stewed ham with fish maw,

0:17:29.020,0:17:32.320
chicken soup with shark skin,
and flowering cabbage with mushrooms.

0:17:33.140,0:17:35.180
These are all Your Majesty’s favorites.

0:17:35.600,0:17:38.300
These are the most time-consuming to make.

0:17:38.920,0:17:42.460
You must have gotten up before dawn to attend to the kitchen.

0:17:43.700,0:17:46.820
I must supervise the cooking of Your Majesty 's food.

0:17:47.440,0:17:51.280
I feel bad that you put
so much effort into just one meal for me.

0:17:51.980,0:17:55.900
It's my pleasure to spare no effort serving Your Majesty.

0:17:58.420,0:18:01.280
Your Majesty must be hungry after
half a day reviewing memorandums.

0:18:01.540,0:18:03.760
Your Majesty should start with some chicken soup to warm the Stomach.

0:18:08.420,0:18:10.320
Your Majesty seems to have a good appetite today.

0:18:10.340,0:18:11.720
Is there any good news?

0:18:12.020,0:18:13.340
Take a guess.

0:18:14.900,0:18:17.260
Is it because Nian Fu fulfilled Your Majesty's grace

0:18:17.420,0:18:19.860
by suppressing the rebels at Mount Zhuozi?

0:18:21.240,0:18:22.800
You have good sources.

0:18:23.760,0:18:25.380
You were informed very promptly.

0:18:25.380,0:18:27.380
The news of victory arrived early in the morning.

0:18:27.640,0:18:29.460
I am happy for Nian Fu as well.

0:18:30.100,0:18:36.320
Nian Fu did not fail his father's teachings and
 has achieved success beyond his young age.

0:18:37.000,0:18:40.460
All morning I have been happy for Nian Fu's
first military victory.

0:18:40.960,0:18:43.820
How does Your Majesty intend to reward him?

0:18:43.880,0:18:48.040
Since you appreciate his hard work, I will reward him
silver and Four Treasures of the Study.

0:18:48.700,0:18:51.240
He is a man of the battlefields.

0:18:51.280,0:18:52.560
He wouldn't care for these.

0:18:52.560,0:18:54.560
So what do your suggest?

0:18:55.500,0:18:58.320
My brother's eldest son, Nian Bin,
has already been awarded a noble title.

0:18:58.320,0:19:02.740
Although Nian Fu is his second son,
he is as gallant as his brother.

0:19:03.480,0:19:06.400
What if Your Majesty also rewards him with a title?

0:19:06.940,0:19:10.520
So they will be of one heart in serving Your Majesty.

0:19:11.040,0:19:16.540
Nian Fu is very young, and this is his first military achievement.

0:19:17.220,0:19:21.060
It's too early to grant him a title.

0:19:22.040,0:19:24.540
He'll have to wait for a couple of years.

0:19:24.580,0:19:27.020
Your Majesty must care more about
my brother's opinion than mine.

0:19:27.620,0:19:29.320
If my brother had made this suggestion

0:19:29.500,0:19:32.920
Your Majesty would say he is acknowledging
the achievement of a warrior.

0:19:33.580,0:19:35.660
But if I make the same suggestion,

0:19:36.020,0:19:37.860
Your Majesty seems to think it's just a woman's short-sighted view.

0:19:38.640,0:19:41.440
Did your brother come to seek a reward for Nian Fu ?

0:19:42.460,0:19:44.700
My brother does adore Nian Fu the most.

0:19:45.020,0:19:47.080
But this is my own idea.

0:19:53.680,0:19:55.460
Let's eat.

0:20:10.260,0:20:11.680
All right.

0:20:12.060,0:20:13.760
All right.

0:20:14.040,0:20:17.920
I will reward your brother the first-order hereditary title

0:20:19.200,0:20:21.200
to be passed on to Nian Fu.

0:20:21.320,0:20:22.780
How's that?

0:20:24.320,0:20:26.540
Your Majesty.

0:20:26.900,0:20:30.020
You Majesty wouldn't agree until I got mad.

0:20:30.520,0:20:32.780
But I don't like being mad at you.

0:20:42.720,0:20:44.520
Your Majesty.

0:20:47.120,0:20:49.480
My Lady, here is the medicine.

0:20:50.360,0:20:54.000
My Lady, the medicine seems to be helpful.

0:20:56.020,0:20:57.880
The weather has been hot and cold.

0:20:58.500,0:21:01.020
It slows down my recovery.

0:21:01.480,0:21:03.280
"Recovering from sickness is like pulling silk from a cocoon."

0:21:03.280,0:21:04.720
It takes time.

0:21:04.720,0:21:08.080
As long as you nurse and nourish yourself,
My Lady, you will surely get well.

0:21:10.460,0:21:11.680
My Lady,

0:21:11.820,0:21:15.060
His Majesty wishes to see you in his
West Chamber at a quarter past one.

0:21:15.920,0:21:16.900
Thank you, sir.

0:21:16.900,0:21:18.320
Allow me to take my leave, My Lady.

0:21:18.340,0:21:19.480
Goodbye.

0:21:25.760,0:21:29.220
When was this memorandum from Nian Gengyao sent in?

0:21:31.020,0:21:33.720
About lunch time.

0:21:34.360,0:21:38.580
Consort Fleur has just sought a reward for Nian Fu at lunch.

0:21:40.760,0:21:47.500
And Nian Gengyao has sent in his request for rewarding
the worthy soldiers in the Mount Zhuozi Campaign.

0:21:49.120,0:21:51.960
They are "ploughing the same furrow."

0:21:53.820,0:21:54.920
Su Peisheng.

0:21:55.100,0:21:56.240
Your Majesty.

0:21:56.500,0:21:59.460
You will lose your head if this is how you do your job!

0:22:00.960,0:22:03.880
Your Majesty, my offence deserves death.

0:22:05.200,0:22:09.020
I beg Your Highness would enlighten
my ignorant mind what I did wrong.

0:22:09.560,0:22:11.320
Your eyes are not sharp enough.

0:22:12.480,0:22:14.920
There are people inside the palace
trading information with the outside.

0:22:14.920,0:22:16.600
Yet you didn't know anything about it.

0:22:16.840,0:22:19.320
You have been as foolish as I have.

0:22:20.840,0:22:22.660
I entreat Your Majesty's forgiveness.

0:22:24.200,0:22:26.200
I beg Your Majesty would spare my life.

0:22:26.260,0:22:28.460
I will surely keep an eye out from now!

0:22:28.800,0:22:33.060
I will let you keep your head to atone for yourself.

0:22:34.420,0:22:35.680
Get up.

0:22:35.680,0:22:37.620
I thank Your Majesty.

0:22:43.220,0:22:47.180
Your Majesty ... Please have some tea and calm down.

0:22:49.380,0:22:51.180
Bring Lady Sourire here.

0:22:51.640,0:22:52.700
Yes.

0:23:10.060,0:23:11.980
Take a look at this.

0:23:12.640,0:23:14.200
I dare not interfere in state affairs.

0:23:14.220,0:23:16.700
This is a family matter. You have my permission.

0:23:26.100,0:23:29.920
Your Majesty, Zhao Zhiyuan impeached my father?

0:23:30.640,0:23:34.580
He accuses your father of
disrespecting 
an honorable official and disobeying me.

0:23:35.060,0:23:37.080
His so-called disrespect ...

0:23:37.260,0:23:40.540
is referring to the fact that he 
did 
not kneel to General Nian like other officials.

0:23:41.260,0:23:44.340
Everyone believed that because I hold Nian Gengyao in high esteem,

0:23:44.520,0:23:48.860
they had to show utmost deference 
to him as if it were obedience to me.

0:23:49.920,0:23:53.360
Your Majesty thinks highly of General Nian
for his contribution to the country.

0:23:53.980,0:23:57.060
But however significant his contribution is,

0:23:57.160,0:23:59.660
General Nian is but a servant 
to the imperial family,

0:23:59.700,0:24:01.640
and officials like my father kneel 
only to their emperors and lords.

0:24:01.640,0:24:04.560
Do you believe I think too highly of Nian Gengyao?

0:24:04.900,0:24:06.300
I dare not.

0:24:06.300,0:24:09.320
I only think that no matter how highly 
Your Majesty values Nian Gengyao,

0:24:09.640,0:24:12.880
he wouldn't dare be arrogant enough to despise his peers.

0:24:13.680,0:24:16.860
Besides, Zhao Zhiyuan is the Review Director
of the Ministry of Public Works.

0:24:17.180,0:24:20.860
Why is he interfering on etiquette rather than tending to his own duties?

0:24:21.220,0:24:24.000
He always "sings the praises" of Nian Gengyao.

0:24:27.140,0:24:30.800
I will carefully consider the
 implications of his memorandum.

0:24:46.260,0:24:48.620
Please be patient, My Lady.

0:24:49.560,0:24:52.320
His Majesty is talking with Lady Sourire.

0:24:52.860,0:24:54.380
Since His Majesty is busy,

0:24:54.500,0:24:56.620
I don't mind waiting for a bit longer.

0:24:59.420,0:25:02.080
Allow me to inform His Majesty one more time.

0:25:02.080,0:25:03.680
Thank you, sir.

0:25:08.820,0:25:10.040
Your Majesty.

0:25:11.020,0:25:11.960
What is it?

0:25:12.160,0:25:14.680
Attendant An has been waiting outside for an hour.

0:25:14.920,0:25:16.620
I'm busy right now.

0:25:16.940,0:25:19.200
Your Majesty, Lingrong is still recovering from her cough.

0:25:19.520,0:25:21.700
It's windy today and she shouldn't be waiting outside.

0:25:21.700,0:25:24.180
Will Your Majesty allow me to leave now?

0:25:24.280,0:25:26.480
But we haven’t finished the conversation.

0:25:26.760,0:25:28.320
- Su Peisheng.
- Yes.

0:25:28.640,0:25:32.080
Tell Attendant An that I can't spare any time to see her.

0:25:32.440,0:25:34.360
Tell her to go back and have a good rest.

0:25:34.500,0:25:35.600
Yes.

0:25:40.580,0:25:43.500
My Lady... I’m terribly sorry.

0:25:44.260,0:25:46.140
His Majesty requests you go back.

0:25:46.320,0:25:50.640
His Majesty is with Lady Sourire ... and not able to see you.

0:25:52.260,0:25:55.700
Sourire provides enough company for His Majesty.

0:25:56.080,0:25:57.820
I’ll go now.

