0:26:21.580,0:26:24.440
My Lady, you were standing in the cold wind for so long.

0:26:24.660,0:26:26.860
It made your cough worse.

0:26:30.940,0:26:32.600
I deserve it.

0:26:33.580,0:26:35.660
I already knew that Lady Sourire was inside.

0:26:36.120,0:26:40.340
But I insisted on waiting and making a fool of myself.

0:26:42.480,0:26:43.840
What was in Lady Sourire's mind?

0:26:43.920,0:26:45.880
She knows you are unwell.

0:26:46.580,0:26:49.860
She should have informed you earlier that His Majesty was busy.

0:26:50.180,0:26:53.120
But she would rather leave you outside waiting in the wind.

0:26:55.080,0:26:58.040
My Lady, you must be feeling cold.
Here's the hand warmer.

0:27:06.000,0:27:08.140
Your Highness, news came in that

0:27:08.160,0:27:12.280
Lady Sourire’s father has been demoted
to the lower fifth rank in the Censorate.

0:27:13.960,0:27:15.400
Yes, Your Highness.

0:27:15.400,0:27:20.360
Lady Sourire has been distinguished among the
new concubines because of her family background.

0:27:21.240,0:27:24.720
Now that her father is demoted, I wonder
if she will still hold her head high.

0:27:24.980,0:27:27.220
Zhao Zhiyuan is competent.

0:27:28.120,0:27:31.380
He took the hint from me and my brother
and staged the impeachment.

0:27:32.680,0:27:36.900
It appears that Lady Sourire now carries
little weight in His Majesty's heart.

0:27:37.980,0:27:41.500
Her freshness as a new concubine has expired.

0:27:42.540,0:27:45.020
That's true. She can't compare to Your Highness.

0:27:45.020,0:27:47.520
Your Highness has been favored by His Majesty all along.

0:27:48.020,0:27:52.320
I heard that His Majesty has only seen her once lately.

0:27:58.020,0:28:02.720
If she was a course in a meal, she 
would have become stale and cold.

0:28:03.580,0:28:08.620
And it's up to Your Highness 
when to take away the plate.

0:28:20.040,0:28:21.480
The soup is getting cold, My Lady.

0:28:21.540,0:28:23.140
You didn't eat any.

0:28:23.520,0:28:26.100
I feel upset. I have no appetite.

0:28:26.680,0:28:29.720
My Lady, you must be feeling upset about ... father.

0:28:30.300,0:28:32.400
But you have to care for your health.

0:28:34.160,0:28:35.760
What's the point of feeling upset?

0:28:35.960,0:28:37.520
It is His Majesty’s decree.

0:28:38.500,0:28:40.400
My Lady, your appetite has been low lately.

0:28:40.520,0:28:42.120
Shall I send for Dr Wen?

0:28:42.380,0:28:43.820
No.

0:28:44.060,0:28:46.460
Dr Wen is busy taking care of Meizhuang.

0:28:47.620,0:28:51.180
Perhaps I've eaten too much greasy food lately.

0:28:54.140,0:28:57.140
I feel tired. I'm going to bed now.

0:28:57.880,0:29:01.000
You've become a sleepy kitten, My Lady.

0:29:03.520,0:29:06.920
Although it is spring now, I still feel cold all over.

0:29:08.320,0:29:11.300
Go fill a hot water warmer for me.

0:29:15.900,0:29:18.180
His Majesty selected you for the night, My Lady.

0:29:18.280,0:29:20.360
You must look your best.

0:29:21.800,0:29:23.600
I went to the Palace of Pearl Jade.

0:29:24.880,0:29:26.580
I feel so sorry for Sourire.

0:29:27.160,0:29:29.220
I don't know how she could sleep.

0:29:29.600,0:29:31.480
Lady Sourire’s father was demoted.

0:29:32.080,0:29:34.280
She must be in distress,

0:29:35.320,0:29:38.480
worrying about everyone laughing at her.

0:29:39.340,0:29:41.880
So she found an excuse to avoid seeing people.

0:29:42.760,0:29:46.160
Sourire was always in high favor with His Majesty.

0:29:46.860,0:29:49.640
What a surprise!

0:29:50.140,0:29:51.920
You are still being kind to her, My Lady.

0:29:52.160,0:29:54.920
She kept you waiting outside the Hall of Mental Cultivation the other day.

0:29:55.140,0:29:56.820
Why do you feel sorry for her?

0:29:56.820,0:29:59.980
Coua, to tell you the truth,

0:30:00.400,0:30:04.260
Not only do I feel sorry, but also relieved.

0:30:04.660,0:30:06.200
Relieved?

0:30:06.380,0:30:08.320
She is better than me in every way.

0:30:08.320,0:30:11.020
She gained more favor from His Majesty

0:30:12.260,0:30:14.660
and has a better family background.

0:30:15.020,0:30:16.960
But now that her father is demoted

0:30:17.340,0:30:20.600
I no longer feel that our situations are so far apart.

0:30:21.780,0:30:24.140
She's no longer distantly above me.

0:30:24.860,0:30:26.480
My Lady, I’m sorry you felt that way.

0:30:26.640,0:30:29.060
I'm the one carrying an imperial heir.
Not Attendant An!

0:30:29.880,0:30:31.900
Why does His Majesty only see Attendant An?

0:30:32.380,0:30:35.040
Isn't she being a minx and taking advantage of my pregnancy?

0:30:35.420,0:30:38.560
Let her be, My Lady.
Lady Fuca always bullies the weak.

0:30:39.020,0:30:43.760
I haven't stopped hearing spiteful words since
moving into the Palace of Prolonging Happiness.

0:30:44.240,0:30:45.660
This is nothing new.

0:30:45.660,0:30:46.740
Yes, My Lady.

0:30:47.700,0:30:49.320
Spring is coming and it's getting warmer.

0:30:49.320,0:30:50.880
Have you been feeling better?

0:30:51.080,0:30:53.960
I thank Your Majesty for asking.
I have been feeling much better.

0:30:54.560,0:30:57.080
Now that Consort Fleur assists
 in the palace affairs

0:30:57.320,0:30:59.620
I have more time to myself.

0:31:00.040,0:31:05.600
You handed over the palace affairs to her
when your migraines became so severe.

0:31:06.380,0:31:09.420
Before I announced it, the concubines had
already started to report to Consort Fleur,

0:31:09.420,0:31:11.700
just as if they could "tell autumn from the falling leaves".

0:31:12.920,0:31:16.640
Consort Fleur is young  ... and efficient.

0:31:17.400,0:31:19.380
Consort Fleur always assisted with the palace affairs.

0:31:19.480,0:31:21.240
She's experienced in the responsibilities.

0:31:22.540,0:31:24.260
The imperial harem is finally in harmony.

0:31:24.360,0:31:27.440
It would be inappropriate for me to keep
Consort Fleur out of palace management.

0:31:28.080,0:31:31.680
Consort Fleur made undeniable contributions to stop the plague.

0:31:32.300,0:31:36.040
And she is more prudent and decorous now.

0:31:36.620,0:31:39.380
It's about time to reinstate her authority in palace management.

0:31:39.740,0:31:41.400
I will follow Your Majesty's decision.

0:31:42.000,0:31:46.700
But there's something I wish to mention about Lady Sourire.

0:31:46.720,0:31:48.800
I know what you want to say.

0:31:49.120,0:31:51.840
I have punished Lady Sourire's father for his own mistake.

0:31:52.280,0:31:53.860
That does not affect Lady Sourire.

0:31:54.060,0:31:56.280
Your Majesty draws a clear line between the court and the harem,

0:31:56.280,0:31:58.560
but concubines don't always do so.

0:31:59.140,0:32:01.440
Your Majesty has always been very fond of Lady Sourire.

0:32:01.620,0:32:04.900
But now the concubines joke about her for what her father did.

0:32:06.080,0:32:10.040
If Your Majesty feels sympathetic for her,
please go visit her tonight.

0:32:10.920,0:32:14.460
But you told me that Attendant An missed me, didn't you?

0:32:15.980,0:32:19.340
I have already selected Attendant An for tonight.

0:32:20.160,0:32:22.740
Your Majesty has been 
buried in state affairs.

0:32:22.920,0:32:25.940
How can any concubine not miss Your Majesty?

0:32:26.520,0:32:30.240
However, Attendant An has always been very close with Lady Sourire.

0:32:31.140,0:32:34.980
She will understand Your Majesty's sympathy for Lady Sourire.

0:32:36.900,0:32:42.440
That will be good. I don't want Lady Sourire
to feel upset because of her father.

0:32:42.840,0:32:44.060
Su Peisheng.

0:32:45.200,0:32:46.300
Your Majesty.

0:32:46.300,0:32:50.940
Announce that Lady Sourire will
stay in the Hall of Mental Cultivation tonight.

0:32:51.460,0:32:52.860
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:33:05.280,0:33:07.840
My Lady, the Phoenix Carriage will be here soon.

0:33:07.840,0:33:09.560
Please be patient.

0:33:13.740,0:33:15.540
His Majesty rarely selects you for the night.

0:33:15.540,0:33:17.640
You must dress nicely ...

0:33:17.860,0:33:20.740
Otherwise His Majesty won't be interested in selecting you again.

0:33:21.260,0:33:22.740
Don't worry, Lady Fuca.

0:33:22.840,0:33:26.740
I will certainly convey to His Majesty that you miss him.

0:33:27.240,0:33:29.320
Are you laughing about me not being chosen to see His Majesty?

0:33:29.320,0:33:33.320
Why would I dare to? I just can't bear
seeing you distressed, missing His Majesty.

0:33:33.740,0:33:35.740
So I wish to speak to His Majesty for you.

0:33:35.740,0:33:37.100
How funny!

0:33:37.340,0:33:42.100
I'm carrying His Majesty's child.
I can see His Majesty whenever I want to.

0:33:42.340,0:33:43.760
You surely can.

0:33:43.880,0:33:48.320
But the next time you call for His Majesty,
better not say it's a "fetal disorder."

0:33:48.920,0:33:51.180
His Majesty will be annoyed if he hears that too much.

0:33:51.400,0:33:53.020
How dare you ...

0:33:56.440,0:33:59.920
Peace to Lady Fuca.
Peace to Attendant An.

0:34:00.640,0:34:02.880
What brings you here, Mr Su?

0:34:03.800,0:34:08.020
My lady, at His Majesty's behest,
you won't be serving him tonight.

0:34:08.560,0:34:11.360
But His Majesty selected me for tonight!

0:34:11.840,0:34:13.560
Yes, My Lady.

0:34:14.060,0:34:17.000
But His Majesty called for Lady Sourire just now.

0:34:17.640,0:34:20.960
The Phoenix Carriage has brought
Lady Sourire to the Hall of Mental Cultivation.

0:34:22.180,0:34:25.260
It's not unusual that His Majesty changes his mind.

0:34:26.520,0:34:32.720
My Lady, perhaps His Majesty wishes you to have a good rest and recover from your cough sooner.

0:34:33.500,0:34:34.740
Thank you, Mr Su.

0:34:35.780,0:34:37.520
Allow me to take my leave.

0:34:42.500,0:34:46.100
It seems that I have overestimated Attendant An.

0:34:46.720,0:34:49.280
Now I don't even expect you will have a "next time."

0:34:50.540,0:34:51.760
What a shame.

0:34:51.860,0:34:53.620
You have dressed up so nicely

0:34:53.800,0:34:55.800
but His Majesty wouldn't even bother to look at you.

0:34:56.260,0:34:58.220
He selected you and regretted it.

0:34:59.820,0:35:02.460
However, you and Sourire are like sisters.

0:35:03.080,0:35:05.240
You two can take turns serving His Majesty.

0:35:05.820,0:35:08.380
It's no different.

0:35:09.380,0:35:13.780
But it's surprising that His Majesty would see her
when her father has just been demoted.

0:35:15.200,0:35:20.160
You've got a lot to learn from her, Lingrong.

0:35:30.620,0:35:32.720
Why ...

0:35:33.940,0:35:37.120
Why must she steal from me?

0:35:38.260,0:35:41.500
You've been losing weight

0:35:41.760,0:35:43.920
and have been more quiet with me.

0:35:46.280,0:35:49.320
Perhaps it's just springtime fatigue.

0:35:50.380,0:35:52.680
Try to be more active even if you feel tired.

0:35:53.240,0:35:55.200
We are more likely to get sick in the spring.

0:35:56.300,0:35:57.700
Your Majesty,

0:35:58.860,0:36:01.360
Lady Fuca feels uncomfortable due to fetal movement.

0:36:02.620,0:36:05.880
She wishes Your Majesty could keep her company.

0:36:06.620,0:36:07.980
Your Majesty should go.

0:36:08.420,0:36:10.040
I will be all right.

0:36:11.500,0:36:13.820
Ask the imperial doctors to take care of her.

0:36:14.320,0:36:15.400
Yes.

0:36:17.320,0:36:19.520
This is Lady Fuca's first time being pregnant.

0:36:20.200,0:36:22.660
Your Majesty should spend more time with her.

0:36:22.900,0:36:25.120
I appreciate your consideration.

0:36:27.300,0:36:30.360
You should stay here and go back tomorrow.

0:36:31.120,0:36:33.720
It's too cold to travel in the middle of the night.

0:36:34.660,0:36:35.700
Yes.

0:36:48.300,0:36:51.260
Peace and grace to Your Majesties.

0:36:51.560,0:36:52.680
You may rise.

0:36:52.680,0:36:54.300
I thank Your Majesty.

0:36:57.200,0:36:58.620
You look unwell.

0:36:58.680,0:37:00.540
Sit down quickly.

0:37:01.940,0:37:04.260
You've got dark circles under your eyes

0:37:05.400,0:37:08.260
I heard that Lady Fuca invited Your Majesty last night.

0:37:08.820,0:37:10.360
Did she feel unwell?

0:37:10.560,0:37:11.700
She was fine.

0:37:12.600,0:37:14.640
Lady Fuca was petulant last night.

0:37:15.460,0:37:18.100
She was complaining that I arrived late and she was feeling nauseous.

0:37:18.380,0:37:19.720
That gave me a headache.

0:37:21.320,0:37:24.120
The plague has been under control in the palace

0:37:24.120,0:37:26.160
to which Consort Fleur made undeniable contributions.

0:37:26.180,0:37:30.640
Therefore I restore her authority to assist in palace management.

0:37:34.460,0:37:36.280
I thank Your Majesty.

0:37:36.660,0:37:41.560
You must fulfill the duties of a Consort and aid the Empress.

0:37:43.060,0:37:44.740
Congratulations, Fleur.

0:37:46.980,0:37:50.420
Concubine Estime has been serving me for over eight years.

0:37:51.540,0:37:54.920
For her dedication to the palace and gentle temperament,

0:37:55.620,0:37:58.060
she will be promoted to Consort.

0:38:01.440,0:38:04.340
Are you too happy to remember to say anything?

0:38:06.760,0:38:08.820
I ... humbly thank Your Majesty.

0:38:09.060,0:38:11.760
Your promotion ceremony will be held on the 19th of next month.

0:38:12.320,0:38:15.180
You entered the palace in the same year as Consort Fleur.

0:38:15.580,0:38:17.640
You are familiar with palace affairs.

0:38:18.120,0:38:23.340
You will aid Consort Fleur in lightening the burden on the Empress.

0:38:23.800,0:38:27.220
I will commit myself to assisting Her Majesty.

0:38:27.740,0:38:29.440
You may rise.

0:38:30.420,0:38:32.420
Congratulations, Consort Estime.

0:38:34.400,0:38:36.940
The scholars in Henan Province are
refusing to take the imperial examination.

0:38:37.620,0:38:39.980
So I will visit Henan tomorrow.

0:38:40.620,0:38:43.580
The Empress will be in charge of the palace affairs

0:38:44.340,0:38:46.540
with assistance from Consort Fleur and  Consort Estime.

0:38:47.020,0:38:51.120
Don't worry, Your Majesty. I will do my utmost.

0:39:01.280,0:39:02.560
Madam.

0:39:03.460,0:39:05.340
I bow in respect before My Lady.

0:39:05.640,0:39:08.900
I heard His Majesty asked you to serve Meizhuang until her full recovery.

0:39:09.220,0:39:10.960
That must be hard work for you, Madam.

0:39:11.020,0:39:13.960
I do not deserve you saying that, My Lady.

0:39:14.520,0:39:17.020
Lady Vertu has been much better.

0:39:23.020,0:39:26.160
Meizhuang, how are you feeling to today?

0:39:26.440,0:39:28.620
I feel a bit better.

0:39:28.900,0:39:30.000
(We are so happy for Your Highness!)

0:39:30.100,0:39:33.660
Why are people talking loudly outside? What happened?

0:39:34.220,0:39:36.220
His Majesty promoted Concubine Estime to Consort.

0:39:36.560,0:39:38.340
Everyone is here to extend their congratulations.

0:39:38.540,0:39:41.220
It's also wonderful that you have been reinstated as Lady Vertu.

0:39:41.620,0:39:43.780
What difference does it make to me?

0:39:44.160,0:39:46.020
It's just a title.

0:39:46.320,0:39:50.940
You have been sick and suffered terribly during the confinement.

0:39:51.780,0:39:53.380
I understand that you feel upset.

0:39:53.620,0:39:57.140
If I say that that I meant it, will you believe me?

0:39:58.680,0:40:02.240
Since you feel better today, why don't we go out for a walk?

0:40:02.680,0:40:04.400
I don't want to go out.

0:40:04.780,0:40:06.340
It annoys me to see people.

0:40:06.340,0:40:09.480
I have peace and quiet in my chamber.

0:40:12.380,0:40:15.340
Nice seeing you here, Dr. Wen.
I haven't had a chance to thank you.

0:40:15.440,0:40:17.960
Meizhuang owes a lot to your excellent care.

0:40:18.260,0:40:19.700
I don't deserve the credit, My Lady.

0:40:19.780,0:40:21.960
It was the imperial doctors who found the remedy.

0:40:22.360,0:40:24.340
I only made small contributions.

0:40:25.680,0:40:30.500
Dr. Wen is being modest. Everyone in the
Imperial Infirmary knows you have excellent medical skills.

0:40:36.900,0:40:39.280
Why didn't anyone announce Dr. Wen's arrival?

0:40:39.280,0:40:42.260
It's so impolite of me with my hair disheveled and my face unwashed.

0:40:42.800,0:40:44.860
You're beautiful regardless.

0:40:45.280,0:40:47.180
When Xi Shi [an ancient beauty] was walking painfully and grimacing,

0:40:47.260,0:40:50.200
Dong Shi [an ugly woman] still wished to look like her and imitated her walk.

0:40:50.200,0:40:52.920
A beauty is a beauty whether she's sick or not.

0:40:53.660,0:40:57.960
Besides, Dr. Wen has been taking care of you
and knows you well.

0:40:58.240,0:41:00.060
We can forgo the formalities.

0:41:00.380,0:41:04.240
I appreciate your thoughtful and thorough care, Dr. Wen.

0:41:08.820,0:41:11.000
My Lady, you have been only eating porridge with pickles.

0:41:11.000,0:41:12.660
Although they are light and easy to digest,

0:41:12.660,0:41:14.460
they are not nourishing enough.

0:41:14.600,0:41:17.420
May I recommend some dietary therapies for you, My Lady?

0:41:18.060,0:41:20.760
I notice that Lady Sourire also looks a bit tired.

0:41:20.860,0:41:23.760
I recommend lamb stewed with ejiao [meat gelatin] from Dong’e.

0:41:23.760,0:41:25.660
It will enrich blood and qi.

0:41:25.800,0:41:27.620
Thank you for thinking of me.

0:41:27.920,0:41:30.560
You always inspire others to think of you.

0:41:31.600,0:41:33.720
Am I right, Dr. Wen?

0:41:34.860,0:41:36.880
It is my duty.

0:41:37.380,0:41:40.580
If you allow me, My Ladies,
I will go write the prescriptions now.

0:41:45.600,0:41:47.640
You must be tired from all the talking.

0:41:48.100,0:41:50.000
You should take a nap.

0:41:51.300,0:41:54.720
You don't look very well today. What's wrong?

0:41:55.180,0:41:58.060
Nothing. I didn't sleep well last night.

0:41:58.620,0:42:00.600
Although I've been "trapped in a well",

0:42:00.600,0:42:03.820
I can still see how the weather is changing outside.

0:42:04.700,0:42:08.080
Consort Fleur is now back to power again.

0:42:09.340,0:42:12.520
Consort Fleur regained her authority in palace management.

0:42:14.000,0:42:17.560
All our efforts are now in vain.

